Can’t hang out, I’ve got vip darshan plans 😌🙏🏻

🕉 Omkareshwar
There was something so calming about just being there. Surrounded by chants, temple bells, and faith. Omkareshwar felt like quiet strength, like my prayers were heard before I even spoke them.

🔥 Mahakaleshwar
The Bhasma Aarti at Mahakaleshwar was unlike anything I’ve ever experienced. Intense, sacred, and overwhelming. I had tears in my eyes. The energy in that moment? Divine.

Grateful and so blessed to have experienced both these powerful Jyotirlingas. It’s a feeling I’ll carry with me forever. ✨🤍

4/12✔️
